## Core workflow

```
Discovery (P1.A)          → /product:init
    ↓
Planning (P1.B)           → /product:plan
    ↓
Feature definition (P2.A) → /product:feature <FM-id>
    ↓ (if has_ui)
UI design (P2.5)          → /design:start <FM-id>
    ↓
Handoff generation        → /product:handoff <FM-id>
    ↓
External implementation   → via Integrator adapter to cc-sdd/Kiro/etc.
```

