## Key commands

### Product (D1 + D2-Behavioral)

- `/product:init [--deep]` — Discovery from idea to HYP (~30-90 min Quick / 2-4h Deep)
- `/product:plan` — MVP scope, Roadmap, Release plan, FM skeletons
- `/product:feature <FM-id>` — enrich FM to behavioral spec (SC, BR, LC, VC, IC)
- `/product:feature "<idea>"` — create new FM bottom-up
- `/product:handoff <FM-id> [--mode draft|production]` — universal snapshot for external tool
- `/product:status` — dashboard of `.product/` state
- `/product:validate` — on-demand full validation
- `/product:da-review <FM-id>` — adversarial business review (6 lenses)
- `/product:drift-check` — structural self-audit against original PS/HYP/MVP
- `/product:patterns` — meta-linter for recurring anti-patterns
- `/product:validation-tune` — propose project-local validation tuning
- `/product:lesson "<...>"` — atomic self-correction: find→fix→record a corrective LESSON-* (use the instant an error is self-detected; non-deferrable)

### Design (D2-B04, conditional on `has_ui: true`)

- `/design:start <FM-id>` — P2.5 orchestrator
- `/design:iterate <MK-id>` — continuation
- `/design:export <FM-id>` — prepare for handoff §10

### Integrator (infrastructure)

- `/integrator:research <need>` — find tools (read-only)
- `/integrator:add <tool>` — install and configure
- `/integrator:map` — current PMO coverage
- `/integrator:status` — full overview
- `/integrator:verify` — consistency check
- `/integrator:debug <error>` — diagnose + fix

### Ecosystem (meta)

- `/ecosystem:verify` — installation health check
- `/ecosystem:update` — sync ecosystem to latest version (preserves `.product/` + config; timestamped backup by default; `--dry-run` to preview)
- `/ecosystem:meta-feedback` — capture systemic ecosystem defects into the upstream outbox (escalated from `/product:validation-tune`)

