## Conventions

### What IS committed to git

- `.product/**` — all artifacts (source of truth)
- `.product/.da-findings/` — DA review history
- `.product/handoffs/` — handoff snapshots
- `.claude/integrator/active-tools.yaml` — team-shared tool config
- `.claude/integrator/pmo-mapping.yaml` — PMO coverage map
- `.claude/integrator/contracts/` — active contracts
- `.claude/integrator/tool-docs/` — tool documentation
- `.claude/integrator/project-journal.md` — decision history
- `.claude/product.yaml` — project config
- `CLAUDE.md` — this file

### What is NOT committed (gitignored)

- `.env` and any secrets
- `.claude/integrator/secrets/`
- `.product/.sessions/` — ephemeral session state
- `.product/.pending/` — transient queues
- `.claude/integrator/baseline.yaml` — rescanned per invocation

### Artifact naming

- Singleton: `<TYPE>.md` — e.g., `problem.md`, `mvp-scope.md`, `glossary.md`
- Enumerable: `<PREFIX>-<NNN>-<slug>.md` — e.g., `SEG-001-freelancers.md`, `FM-003-revisions-inbox.md`
- IDs are 3-digit with leading zeros: `SEG-001`, `FM-042`, `BR-010`

### SC numbering for flow types

- `SC-NNN` — main flow
- `SC-NNNa`, `SC-NNNb` — alternative flows of main SC-NNN
- `SC-NNNe1`, `SC-NNNe2` — error flows of main SC-NNN

